data.description: You won't want to miss this cozy Crestview home completely full of upgrades! Gray shaker cabinets, white quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and LVP throughout the living room and bathrooms (all updated in 2021) make this home completely move-in ready. Other 2021 updates include the roof, hot water heater, wiring, plumbing, light fixtures, and more! Located on a corner lot of a quiet street, this home boasts the perfect opportunity to enjoy a relaxing evening in the large backyard. Conveniently located to Eglin AFB, Duke Field, and 7th SFG.
